{"about_the_game":"<strong><i>FLY LIKE A KID, FEEL LIKE A PILOT! </i></strong><br>Kid Pilot is a flight adventure game where you soar through amazing worlds just by moving your hand. Explore beautiful environments, earn badges, discover secrets, overcome challenging boss fights and become a Top Pilot!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/KP_SteamGif_Dragordito01.gif?t=1720647505\" /><br><br><strong><i>ADVENTURE AWAITS, UNLOCK NEW AIRCRAFTS </i></strong><br>Wander through the skies alongside friendly toys, navigate intricate tiki mazes, or dare to enter the depths of a treacherous volcano. But that\u2019s just the beginning. As you progress, you\u2019ll unlock new planes and worlds to explore. Soon you might even reach the cosmos!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/KP_SteamGif_Parakeet02.gif?t=1720647505\" /><br><br><strong><i>FUN &amp; INTUITIVE FLYING CONTROLS</i></strong><br>When we were kids, we used to play with toy airplanes, the interface was very simple: our hands! Get ready for the most intuitive flying experience you\u00b4ve ever had. With a simple twist of the wrist, you can control your plane and fly anywhere. It feels amazing, experience true freedom!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/KP_SteamGif_Girafloat01.gif?t=1720647505\" /><br><br><strong><i>EPIC BOSS FIGHTS! </i></strong><br>No true adventure is complete without the thrill and challenge of an epic boss fight. In Kid Pilot, you'll earn your wings as a top aviator by facing the danger head on. Will you rise to the occasion as a Master Pilot? The sky's the limit!&quot;<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/KP_SteamGif_Magmanimus02.gif?t=1720647505\" />","achievements":{"highlighted"